  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The programme will enable SMEs to receive payment for their goods immediately after delivering goods and services to their buyers, rather than having to wait for extended periods for payment. This will enable SMEs to unlock working capital they need to manage their businesses, and at a lower rate than alternative financing options. This could also lead to enhanced firm sustainability due to reduced volatility in cash flows.</narrative>
  </description>
